<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8">
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
  <title>Subscription Cancellation Confirmation</title>
  <style>
    body { font-family: Arial, sans-serif; line-height: 1.6; color: #333; max-width: 600px; margin: 0 auto; padding: 20px; }
    .header { background: #6b7280; color: white; padding: 30px; text-align: center; border-radius: 8px 8px 0 0; }
    .content { background: #f9f9f9; padding: 30px; border-radius: 0 0 8px 8px; }
    .cancel-box { background: #f3f4f6; border-left: 4px solid #6b7280; padding: 20px; border-radius: 5px; margin: 20px 0; }
    .info-box { background: white; padding: 20px; border-radius: 5px; margin: 20px 0; }
    .info-row { padding: 10px 0; border-bottom: 1px solid #eee; }
    .button { display: inline-block; background: #667eea; color: white; padding: 12px 30px; text-decoration: none; border-radius: 5px; margin: 20px 0; }
    .footer { text-align: center; color: #666; font-size: 12px; margin-top: 30px; }
  </style>
</head>
<body>
  <div class="header">
    <h1>Subscription Cancelled</h1>
  </div>
  
  <div class="content">
    <p>Hi {{tenantName}},</p>
    
    <p>We have received your cancellation request for your <strong>{{planName}}</strong> subscription.</p>
    
    <div class="cancel-box">
      {{#if cancelImmediately}}
      <p><strong>Your subscription has been cancelled immediately.</strong></p>
      <p>Your service access has ended as of today.</p>
      {{else}}
      <p><strong>Your subscription will remain active until {{serviceEndDate}}.</strong></p>
      <p>After this date, your service access will end.</p>
      {{/if}}
    </div>
    
    <div class="info-box">
      <h3>Cancellation Details</h3>
      <div class="info-row">
        <strong>Plan:</strong> {{planName}}
      </div>
      <div class="info-row">
        <strong>Service End Date:</strong> {{serviceEndDate}}
      </div>
      {{#if cancellationReason}}
      <div class="info-row">
        <strong>Reason:</strong> {{cancellationReason}}
      </div>
      {{/if}}
    </div>
    
    <p>We're sorry to see you go! If you change your mind, you can reactivate your subscription at any time.</p>
    
    <center>
      <a href="{{reactivateUrl}}" class="button">Reactivate Subscription</a>
    </center>
    
    <p>If you have any feedback about your experience or questions about your cancellation, please contact our support team at <a href="mailto:{{supportEmail}}">{{supportEmail}}</a></p>
    
    <p>Thank you for using WhatsApp CRM.</p>
    
    <p>Best regards,<br>The WhatsApp CRM Team</p>
  </div>
  
  <div class="footer">
    <p>Â© 2025 WhatsApp CRM. All rights reserved.</p>
  </div>
</body>
</html>
